<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="section faq-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2 class="section-title faq-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <p class="section-description">Find answers to common questions about renting, selling, and working with Vanier Capital.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-list">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-1">How do I apply for a rental property?</button>
                <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-1">
                    <p>You can browse our available listings on the "For Rent" page. Each listing has an "Inquire Now" button. Once you inquire, our leasing team will guide you through the application process, which includes a background and credit check.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-2">What are your requirements for tenants?</button>
                <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-2">
                    <p>We generally look for a credit score of 600+, verifiable income of at least 3x the monthly rent, and a clean rental history with no prior evictions. Specific requirements may vary by property.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-3">Do you buy homes for cash?</button>
                <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-3">
                    <p>Yes, we purchase homes directly from owners in any condition. This allows you to sell your home quickly without repairs, staging, or agent commissions. Visit our "Sell Your Home" page to get started.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-4">How quickly can you close on a home purchase?</button>
                <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-4">
                    <p>We can typically close in as little as 14-30 days, depending on your timeline. We handle all the paperwork to make the process as smooth as possible.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-5">I am a current tenant. How do I report a maintenance issue?</button>
                <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-5">
                    <p>Please use the tenant portal link provided in your lease agreement to submit maintenance requests. For emergencies, please call our 24/7 support line immediately.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-6">Where does Vanier Capital operate?</button>
                <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-6">
                    <p>We currently own and operate single-family and multifamily communities in select markets with strong growth fundamentals. Check our Portfolio page to see our current footprint.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

